        </a>
        <a href="https://www.consumerfinance.gov/complaint/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="padding: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink);">
          <span class="section-label" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">// file complaint</span>
